OL,3,CChild criminal exploitation and
OL,4,C'cuckooing' to be outlawed in new
OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FChild criminal exploitation and
OL,8,F"cuckooing" are expected to be
OL,9,Fexplicitly outlawed in new legislation
OL,10,Fset to be introduced to Parliament
OL,11,Fnext week.
OL,13,FThe Crime and Policing Bill will also
OL,14,Finclude measures that could see
OL,15,Frestriction orders put on people
OL,16,Fthought to be at risk of exploiting
OL,17,Fchildren for criminal means.
