OL,7,FThe department says that around 14,500
OL,8,Fchildren were identified as being at
OL,9,Frisk of CCE in 2023-24, but that is
OL,10,Flikely to be an underestimated figure.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,13,Fdescribed exploitation of vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople and children as "sickening" and
OL,15,Fsaid "it is vital we do everything in
OL,16,Four power to eradicate if from our
OL,17,Fstreets".
