OL,4,C'cuckooing' to be outlawed in new
OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FShe said that ministers are
OL,8,F"introducing these two offences to
OL,9,Fproperly punish those who prey on
OL,10,Fthem, ensure victims are properly
OL,11,Fprotected and prevent these often
OL,12,Fhidden crimes from occurring in the
OL,13,Ffirst place.
OL,15,F"These steps are vital in our efforts
OL,16,Fto stop the grooming and exploitation
OL,17,Fof children into criminal gangs,
OL,18,Fdeliver on our pledge to halve knife
OL,19,Fcrime in the next decade and work
OL,20,Ftowards our overall mission to make
OL,21,Four streets safer."
