OL,7,FThe cuckooing offence will carry a
OL,8,Fmaximum penalty of five years in
OL,9,Fprison, while the standalone child
OL,10,Fcriminal exploitation offence will
OL,11,Fcarry a maximum sentence of 10 years
OL,12,Fin prison.
