OL,7,F"Many children targeted by adult
OL,8,Fcriminals themselves face punishment
OL,9,Finstead of support. Like too many
OL,10,Fchild victims, they are often ignored
OL,11,Fand overlooked. Their voices and
OL,12,Fexperiences must be listened to, if we
OL,13,Fare to create a child-centric justice
OL,14,Fsystem that puts safeguarding at its
OL,15,Fheart.
